-- Bank of Canada Appoints Three New Advisers to Governor Poloz
-- B y   G r e g   Q u i n n
-- 2013-07-25T18:35:47Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-07-25/bank-of-canada-appoints-three-new-advisers-to-governor-poloz.html
The  Bank of Canada  named three new
advisers to Governor Stephen Poloz, with all of them coming from
within the central bank.  The appointments of Don Coletti, Sharon Kozicki and Carolyn
Wilkins are effective Aug. 26, the Ottawa-based bank said on its
website.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Greg Quinn in Ottawa at 
 gquinn1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
